Preconditions:
The input array `strs` should not be null.
The input array `strs` should not be empty.

Postconditions:
The method should return a list of lists, where each inner list contains a group of anagrams.
The order of the groups in the returned list can be in any order.
Each group in the returned list should contain all the anagrams present in the input array `strs`.
The anagrams within each group should be in the same order as they appear in the input array `strs`.